OL,3,CWelfare concessions to be set out
OL,4,Cahead of crunch vote
OL,6,FThe Government is to set out the
OL,7,Fconcessions it has made to its welfare
OL,8,Freforms in the hope that the climbdown
OL,9,Fon cuts will be enough to shore up
OL,10,Fsupport in a crunch vote.
OL,12,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,13,FKendall said the Bill aims to deliver
OL,14,Fa "fairer, more compassionate system"
OL,15,Fahead of the legislation's second
OL,16,Freading on Tuesday.
OL,18,FThe Government will amend the Bill at
OL,19,Fthe Commons committee stage to put the
OL,20,Fchanges in place.
