OL,3,CWelfare concessions to be set out
OL,4,Cahead of crunch vote
OL,6,FThe original plans restricted
OL,7,Feligibility for the personal
OL,8,Findependence payment (Pip) and cut the
OL,9,Fhealth-related element of universal
OL,10,Fcredit.
OL,12,FThe changes to Pip will now only apply
OL,13,Fto new claims from November 2026.
OL,15,FPlans to cut the health-related
OL,16,Felement of universal credit have also
OL,17,Fbeen rowed back, with all existing
OL,18,Frecipients to have their incomes
OL,19,Fprotected in real terms.
