OL,6,F"This is about delivering a fairer,
OL,7,Fmore compassionate system as part of
OL,8,Four Plan for Change which supports
OL,9,Fpeople to thrive, whatever their
OL,10,Fcircumstances."
OL,12,FSome #300 million in employment
OL,13,Fsupport will also be brought forward
OL,14,Fover the next three years.
OL,16,FThose with severe conditions who are
OL,17,Funlikely to recover ` about 200,000
OL,18,Fpeople ` will not be called for a
OL,19,Freassessment of universal credit.
