OL,6,FLabour MP Rachael Maskell said she
OL,7,Fwould sign the new amendment aiming to
OL,8,Fstop the Bill, saying it was not clear
OL,9,Fhow the promised concessions would be
OL,10,Fbrought in.
OL,12,F"There's no confidence... we're being
OL,13,Fasked to sign a blank check even with
OL,14,Fthese changes," she told the PA news
OL,15,Fagency.
